      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "PharmaCare Ltd. manufactures vaccines, insulin and temperature-sensitive medicines. Products are shipped from Hyderabad to hospitals across India and exported to Singapore and Dubai. The company wants SAP TM to optimize transportation while maintaining cold-chain compliance and improving shipment visibility."
